### Customer Sub Accounts - Create
POST {{SkyRoc_HostAddress}}/api/CustomerSubAccounts
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "companyId": "{{companyId}}",
  "customerId": "{{customerId}}",
  "username": "school_buyer_001",
